/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c1087%2c20220929%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KSHM,111,聲,1087,20220929,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"1087","JDATE":"20220929","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}